Welcome to SCP: Roleplay!

In this world, terrifying or unusual creatures and objects called SCPs roam the earth.
To protect humanity from them, the SCP Foundation was created.
The Foundation conducts experiments to learn more about the SCPs.
The mission of the Foundation is to secure, contain and protect the SCPs.

Play as a Prisoner (Class - D), Scientist, Guard, and unlock more teams as you progress.

Will you assist them or will you bring chaos to the world?

[!] It is important that you read the rules: 
https://devforum.roblox.com/t/scp-roleplay-game-rules/

[NOTE] To access different modes such as Infection, you can use the Modes button on the right side of the menu.

Anime Games.d:
ANIME X SHOWDOWN

Premium Benefits:
- Double base rewards in AFK World

Commands:
!redeem [code]
!join [friend]

Controls:
  - Shift (Hold): Sprint
  - M1: Basic Attack
  - M2: Heavy Attack
  - Space (Hold) + M1 (On Ground): Uptilt
  - Space (Hold) + M1 (In Air): Air Launcher
  - M2 (In Air): Aerial Slam
  - Q: Dash
  - F: Block
  - F (Timed, on specific moves): Perfect Block
  - C: Move Meter Charge
  - R: (when bottom white gauge is full): Evasive
  - X: (When orange icon above moves is visible): Assault Dash

Moves:
  - Not all skills are perfect blockable.
  - Moves cost Move Meter (Blue meter at the top), which you can get back from charging with the C key or landing M1 attacks.

Armor Levels:
  - Super Armor is weaker than Hyper Armor.
  - Super Armor absorbs 50% damage rather than all 100% on non armor-breaking moves.
  - Some skills can BREAK Armor, this means they can cancel an attack with Armor.
  - Hyper Armor Break can cancel Super Armor and Hyper Armor moves.
